Five, The Associated Press misreported the title of the album. 
</P>
<P>
	It is called ``The Unauthorized Biography of Reinhold Messner,''  
not ``The Secret Life of Reinhold Messner.'' 
</P>
<P>
	The AP also erroneously referred to the band as The Ben Folds  
Five. 
  	   	
