<HEADLINE>  Indonesia Leader Concedes Defeat </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	JAKARTA, Indonesia (AP) -- A prominent opposition leader whose  
party was behind in partial election returns conceded defeat today, 
boosting the legitimacy of a key step in Indonesia's democratic 
