<HEADLINE>  Pope Addresses Polish Parliament </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	WARSAW, Poland (AP) -- Pope John Paul II celebrated his  
homeland's decade of freedom today with an unprecedented speech in 
parliament, receiving a hero's welcome from Solidarity and 
ex-communist deputies alike. 
</P>
