<HEADLINE> Delta Air Lines Offers Web Discount </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	ATLANTA (AP) -- Delta Air Lines is offering a 10 percent discount  
on flights to five southeastern U.S. states that are booked through 
the company's Web site. 
</P>
<P>
	The discount, announced Friday, is subject to a three-day  
advance purchase requirement. It applies on economy-class flights 
to Alabama, Florida, Georgia, Mississippi and South Carolina. The 
online promotion lasts through Wednesday. 
</P>
<P>
	Atlanta-based Delta is the region's leading carrier, serving 23  
cities in the five states. 

  	   	
